user_query: A paper about AI regulation that was originally submitted to arXiv.org in June 2022 shows a figure with three axes, where each axis has a label word at both ends. Which of these words is used to describe a type of society in a Physics and Society article submitted to arXiv.org on August 11, 2016?

1.panel_description: Identify June 2022 AI Regulation Paper and Extract Axis Labels

1.handles: Searches for the AI regulation paper submitted to arXiv.org in June 2022 and extracts axis labels from the figure.

input_vars.name: ai_regulation_query
input_vars.description: Query to find the AI regulation paper and extract axis labels.
input_vars.value: Find AI regulation paper submitted to arXiv.org in June 2022 and extract axis labels from the figure.

output_vars.name: axis_labels
output_vars.description: Labels from the three axes in the figure of the AI regulation paper.

2.panel_description: Identify August 2016 Physics and Society Article and Extract Society Descriptions

1.handles: Searches for the Physics and Society article submitted to arXiv.org on August 11, 2016, and extracts society descriptions.

input_vars.name: physics_society_query
input_vars.description: Query to find the Physics and Society article and extract society descriptions.
input_vars.value: Find Physics and Society article submitted to arXiv.org on August 11, 2016, and extract words describing a type of society.

output_vars.name: society_descriptions
output_vars.description: Words used to describe a type of society in the Physics and Society article.

3.panel_description: Cross-reference Axis Labels with Society Descriptions

1.handles: Compares the words from the axis labels of the June 2022 paper with the words describing a type of society in the August 2016 article to find a match.

input_vars.name: axis_labels
input_vars.description: Axis labels from the AI regulation paper.

input_vars.name: society_descriptions
input_vars.description: Society descriptions from the Physics and Society article.

output_vars.name: matching_word
output_vars.description: Word used to describe a type of society that matches an axis label.
